keeper of the bees is a 1947 american drama film directed by william berke and written by robert creighton williams . the film stars dorothy dalton , charles " chic " barry , janet beecher , frank currier , william conklin , frank currier , william conklin , william conklin , george barbier , william conklin , william conklin , charles sellon , and robert benchley . the film was released on june 1 , 1947 , by republic pictures .